          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1690286242637-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1690286242637-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad</strong>,<strong> grated carrot</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to a bowl with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> carrot & coriander salad</strong></p><p>Discard the <strong>clove[s]</strong> from the fragrant rice and cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690286245776-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690286245776-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690286245776-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690286245776-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690286245776-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Bengali-style mustard hake</strong> alongside the<strong> fragrant rice</strong> with the <strong>carrot & coriander salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
